It says simply this.

25:53.442 --> 26:15.211
to have deep loyalty, strong affection or intense dedication to a person cause, belief or activity, often involving giving its significant time, attention, commitment, sometimes prioritizing it over other things, showing faithfulness and believing, being willing to be self-sacrificing for it.

26:15.231 --> 26:17.715
