27:48.418 --> 27:54.827
Petros, little Rock Peter, I will build my church and the gates of hell.

27:55.368 --> 27:58.813
I will build my church on this rock, this massive rock.

27:58.833 --> 28:09.689
I'm not gonna build it on Peter, but I'm building it on Petra, the massive rock, the firm foundation, but he's calling us his people to be the ones to build.

28:10.751 --> 28:11.432
