28:53.641 --> 28:56.484
These believers weren't casual listeners.

28:56.924 --> 29:02.870
They were building their entire lives on the word of God, the truth of God.

29:02.890 --> 29:08.236
With that being said, I wonder again, are you devoted to God?

29:08.276 --> 29:10.578
Are you devoted to His church?

29:11.106 --> 29:15.391
Have you allowed your relationship with God to be more than just a weekend romance?

29:18.674 --> 29:23.159
Are you moving toward all in devotion and dedication?

29:24.761 --> 29:27.564
The early church did not build on emotion or opinion.

29:28.064 --> 29:32.770
