30:33.655 --> 30:37.138
In other words, all scripture is God,

30:37.442 --> 30:38.303
breathed.

30:38.323 --> 30:41.087
Now, to me, that's a whole lot deeper than inspired.

30:41.107 --> 30:44.431
I can inspire somebody.

30:44.471 --> 30:49.338
