31:16.673 --> 31:17.254
Man, let me move on.

31:19.738 --> 31:20.218
Let me move on.

31:21.620 --> 31:23.963
So here, the word inspired is not the greatest.

31:24.023 --> 31:26.507
It's really the word God breathed.

31:27.828 --> 31:29.010
It literally means

31:29.730 --> 31:33.475
Scripture is the very life and the word of God.

31:33.615 --> 31:34.656
It's without error.

31:34.736 --> 31:35.738
It's absolutely true.

31:35.818 --> 31:36.559
It's trustworthy.

31:36.839 --> 31:37.780
It's never wrong.

31:37.880 --> 31:43.828
It's the anchor that we can hold tightly to when everything around us begins to go chaotic.

31:44.008 --> 31:49.535
When every storm rises up against us, Timothy goes on to say that the word of God is useful.

31:49.856 --> 31:54.962
It corrects, it teaches, and it helps us to be prepared and equipped.

31:55.362 --> 32:02.470
for all moments in every area of life to fulfill and do the good works that God said before us.

32:03.891 --> 32:13.302
Come on, this, the Word of God, must be the final authority in every action in every area as we build His church.

32:14.643 --> 32:18.067
