37:20.425 --> 37:24.350
We've got a wellness group that gathers together Tuesdays and Saturdays.

37:25.812 --> 37:37.526
Just moments of living life, sharing burdens, sharing faith, encouraging one another, enhancing purpose.

37:38.747 --> 37:44.274
One, without, I want to encourage you, be a part of something larger

37:44.770 --> 37:45.471
than yourself.

37:46.332 --> 37:55.381
I mean, the moment that you begin to isolate is the moment that you begin to lose sight of what God's doing.

37:57.163 --> 38:07.113
